attributes.description:
KIA RIO 1.4 MT EX
Stunning Rio in excellent condition. Full service history. Central locking, airbag, aircon, radio with bluetooth and USB. Power steering with controls on steering wheel. Electric windows and mirrors. Manual transmission that gives a smooth and comfortable drive for you and your family. Great fuel consumption. reverse camera and sensors to assist with parking. Visit your KIA Konfidence dealership in the Westrand, situated in Wilropark, roodepoort and book this beauty for a test drive. Trade ins accepted. Nationwide delivery.
